text: H100 or H-100 may refer to: * H.100 (computer telephony), a standard for communication between PCI cards in a computer telephony system * H100 series, a diesel multiple unit train in Japan * Heathkit H100, a kit by Heathkit sold assembled as the Zenith Z-100 computer * Hyundai Grace, a minibus or van * Hyundai Porter, a pickup truck * iriver H100 series, a series of hard drive digital audio players produced by iriver * The fourth generation of Toyota HiAce, also known as H100
title: H100
